下面是一个简单的Java爬虫示例，使用OkHttp库发送HTTP请求，获取目标网站的HTML页面：

``` java
import okhttp3.OkHttpClient;
import okhttp3.Request;
import okhttp3.Response;

import java.io.IOException;

public class ChatGPTPageCrawler {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        OkHttpClient client = new OkHttpClient();
        Request request = new Request.Builder()
            .url("https://huggingface.co/spaces/yuntian-deng/ChatGPT")
            .get()
            .addHeader("User-Agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:105.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/105.0")
            .build();

        try {
            Response response = client.newCall(request).execute();
            String html = response.body().string();
            System.out.println(html); // 打印获取到的HTML页面内容
        } catch (IOException e) {
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}
```

